    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the role of Judas Kerioth, a Shemerian oppressed by the corrupt Pleroman government. Since the Time of Tribulation, Judas has longed to join the zealots, a rebel group now in hiding. But when the Pleromans arrest his childhood friend, Lena, on trumped-up charges, he’ll do anything to save her—even face off against the archons, mutated monsters with unimaginable power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330420/extras/aaad148adae5bc3f137b5e01a772cdc5.poster.avif?t=1758220073\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330420/extras/aaad148adae5bc3f137b5e01a772cdc5.webm?t=1758220073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330420/extras/aaad148adae5bc3f137b5e01a772cdc5.mp4?t=1758220073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the first <i>Elohim Eternal</i>, players explored the world of Idin. In <i>Elohim Eternal II: Son of Man</i>, they will venture across the second planet in the kosmeos, Kenoma, a highly advanced, cyberpunk-inspired world on the brink of civil war. Kenoma and its legends draw inspiration from Judaism, Christianity, and Gnosticism.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330420/extras/843e545979eb1cbc9abe6dbf2681d64e.poster.avif?t=1758220073\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330420/extras/843e545979eb1cbc9abe6dbf2681d64e.webm?t=1758220073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330420/extras/843e545979eb1cbc9abe6dbf2681d64e.mp4?t=1758220073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip a myriad of guns, all with their own abilities, stats, and perks. Mix and match guns to gain a tactical advantage over enemies in fast-paced turn-based combat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330420/extras/1b68a6ac2e46900148ffce4fb8232ca5.poster.avif?t=1758220073\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330420/extras/1b68a6ac2e46900148ffce4fb8232ca5.webm?t=1758220073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330420/extras/1b68a6ac2e46900148ffce4fb8232ca5.mp4?t=1758220073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pilot an azar, a huge mecha, in your fight against the Pleromans. Challenge the azar arena and reap the rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is approximately 15 hours long. While not required, completing <i>Elohim Eternal: The Babel Code</i> is recommended for a fuller experience. Unlike video game series, the <i>Elohim Eternal</i> series follows an overarching plot; however, each game in the series does present its own complete story. The game also features a &quot;What Comes Before&quot; feature so you can learn what occurred in games preceding this one. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330420/extras/9e989da38fca5ab00f71b263772a0254.avif?t=1758220073\" width=1038 height=667 /></span></p>",
